    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54B32 3.2L inline-six featuring high-pressure Double VANOS and six individual throttle bodies. This specimen is mechanically flawless, with a documented subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive cooling system overhaul. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, sending power through a variable M differential lock. The chassis retains its factory-spec 50/50 weight distribution, supported by pristine bushings and original-spec Sachs dampers. Finished in Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather, the paint meter readings are consistent across all panels, and the cabin remains free of bolster wear or UV damage. This is a turn-key example for the discerning collector.",
